1. Introduction
Welcome to the Sliding Number Puzzle Game Documentation! This document provides an overview of the sliding number puzzle game, its features, gameplay instructions, installation process, controls, and development details.

2. Game Overview
The sliding number puzzle game is a classic and challenging puzzle where players rearrange numbered tiles to arrange them in sequential order. The objective is to slide the tiles into the correct order, ultimately solving the puzzle.

3. Features
Interactive sliding puzzle gameplay with numbered tiles.
Dynamic tile colors that change with each slide.
Scramble button to shuffle the tiles for a new game.
Adjustable grid size for varying difficulty levels.
Win status display indicating the number of moves taken.
4. Gameplay
Upon starting the game, tiles are initially shuffled.
Slide tiles horizontally or vertically to empty spaces.
Form the correct numerical order to solve the puzzle.
The game is won when the tiles are arranged in sequential order.
5. Installation
To play the game:

Clone or download the game's source code from the GitHub repository.
Open the index.html file in a web browser.
6. Controls
Use the mouse to click on a numbered tile adjacent to the empty space to slide it.
Click the "Scramble" button to shuffle the tiles for a new game.
Use the dropdown menu to select the grid size and adjust difficulty.
7. Development
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript
Code Structure
index.html: The main HTML file containing the game canvas and user interface elements.
styles.css: The CSS file responsible for styling the game and user interface.
script.js: The JavaScript file containing the game logic and functionality.
How to Customize
Adjust the createGame function in script.js to change the grid size and starting arrangement.
Modify the colors array to customize tile colors.
Customize the game's appearance by updating the CSS in styles.css.
Future Enhancements
Timer feature to track time taken to complete the puzzle.
Hint system to assist players in solving the puzzle.
Multiple puzzle themes and customizable tile designs.
